| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1756 — Recovery Inhibition (ALP-001)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 39b3dd67-1c1c-5103-b1ab-39ae6fbd28f3"
